{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"root","type":"group","x":-100,"y":-2800,"width":2200,"height":6000,"label":"SLeads 系统架构 (2026-03-12)"},
		
		{"id":"layer1_group","type":"group","x":-50,"y":-2650,"width":2100,"height":800,"label":"1. 数据源层 (Data Sources)"},
		{"id":"source_pubmed","type":"text","text":"PubMed Search\n\n搜索关键词：\n- Multiplex Immunofluorescence\n- mIF\n- Immunofluorescence\n\n实现：PubMedSearchCollector\n通过 Jina Search API 搜索","x":-30,"y":-2600,"width":400,"height":350},
		{"id":"source_library","type":"text","text":"SingleCellPapers Library\n\nURL: https://single-cell-papers.bioinfo-assist.com\n\n实现：SingleCellPapersCollector\n翻页读取论文库","x":400,"y":-2600,"width":400,"height":350},
		{"id":"source_tender","type":"text","text":"招标网站 (Tender Sources)\n\n计划数据源：\n- 中国政府采购网 ccgp.gov.cn\n- 全国公共资源交易平台 ggzy.gov.cn\n\n实现：TenderCrawler\n关键词：免疫荧光,mIF,病理诊断","x":830,"y":-2600,"width":400,"height":350},
		{"id":"source_multi","type":"text","text":"多模式收集器\n\nMultiModeCollector\n\n功能：\n- 同时运行 Search + Library\n- 自动合并去重\n- 返回统一格式 URL 列表","x":1260,"y":-2600,"width":400,"height":350},
		
		{"id":"layer2_group","type":"group","x":-50,"y":-1750,"width":2100,"height":900,"label":"2. 数据采集层 (Crawlers)"},
		{"id":"crawler_jina_reader","type":"text","text":"Jina Reader Client\n\nAPI: r.jina.ai\n\n功能：\n- URL → Markdown 内容\n- 干净的文本输出\n- 支持各种网站\n\n文件：src/crawlers/jina_client.py","x":-30,"y":-1700,"width":500,"height":400},
		{"id":"crawler_jina_search","type":"text","text":"Jina Search Client\n\nAPI: s.jina.ai\n\n功能：\n- 关键词搜索\n- 发现新 URL\n- 返回搜索结果\n\n文件：src/crawlers/jina_client.py","x":500,"y":-1700,"width":500,"height":400},
		{"id":"crawler_playwright","type":"text","text":"Playwright Client (兜底)\n\n功能：\n- 处理反爬网站\n- 自动检测 Cloudflare\n- 浏览器渲染\n\n文件：src/crawlers/playwright_client.py\n状态：✅ 已实现","x":1030,"y":-1700,"width":500,"height":400},
		{"id":"crawler_fetcher","type":"text","text":"Content Fetcher (统一接口)\n\n功能：\n- 优先使用 Jina Reader\n- 失败自动切换 Playwright\n- 统计成功率\n\n文件：src/crawlers/content_fetcher.py\n状态：✅ 已实现","x":1560,"y":-1700,"width":450,"height":400},
		
		{"id":"layer3_group","type":"group","x":-50,"y":-750,"width":2100,"height":800,"label":"3. 数据处理层 (Processing)"},
		{"id":"process_dedup","type":"text","text":"URL Deduplicator\n\n功能：\n- PMID 去重\n- DOI 去重\n- URL 标准化\n- 多源合并\n\n文件：src/processors/url_deduplicator.py\n状态：✅ 已实现\n测试：4 → 2 (通过)","x":-30,"y":-700,"width":450,"height":400},
		{"id":"process_llm","type":"text","text":"LLM Extractor (GLM-5)\n\nAPI: open.bigmodel.cn\nModel: glm-5\n\n功能：\n- Markdown → 结构化 JSON\n- 提取作者信息\n- 提取单位信息\n\n文件：src/llm/extractor.py\n状态：✅ 已实现","x":450,"y":-700,"width":450,"height":400},
		{"id":"process_rate","type":"text","text":"Rate Limiter\n\n功能：\n- 高峰期 (14:00-18:00): 30秒/请求\n- 非高峰期: 20秒/请求\n- 429 错误自动重试\n\n文件：src/llm/rate_limiter.py\n状态：✅ 已实现","x":930,"y":-700,"width":450,"height":400},
		{"id":"process_pipeline","type":"text","text":"Lead Pipeline\n\n流程：\n1. 检查 URL 是否已爬取\n2. 获取内容\n3. LLM 提取\n4. 评分\n5. 入库\n\n文件：src/pipeline.py\n状态：✅ 已实现","x":1410,"y":-700,"width":580,"height":400},
		
		{"id":"layer4_group","type":"group","x":-50,"y":150,"width":2100,"height":800,"label":"4. 数据存储层 (Storage)"},
		{"id":"db_models","type":"text","text":"数据库模型\n\nPostgreSQL 16+\n\nModels:\n- PaperLead (论文线索)\n- TenderLead (招标线索)\n- CrawledURL (已爬 URL)\n\n文件：src/db/models.py","x":-30,"y":200,"width":600,"height":350},
		{"id":"db_fields","type":"text","text":"PaperLead 字段\n\n- pmid (PubMed ID)\n- doi\n- title (文章标题)\n- published_at (发表时间)\n- name (通讯作者)\n- institution (单位)\n- email (邮箱)\n- source_url (来源链接)\n- grade (等级 A/B/C/D)\n- score (分数 0-100)","x":600,"y":200,"width":550,"height":350},
		{"id":"db_unique","type":"text","text":"去重与增量控制\n\n唯一标识：\n- URL (source_url)\n- PMID\n- DOI\n\n增量控制：\n- crawled_urls 表\n- 已爬 URL 不重复处理\n\n状态：✅ 已实现","x":1180,"y":200,"width":500,"height":350},
		{"id":"db_connection","type":"text","text":"数据库连接\n\n配置：\n- DATABASE_URL 环境变量\n- AsyncPG 异步驱动\n\n连接池：\n- async_session_maker\n- 自动管理会话\n\n文件：src/db/utils.py","x":1710,"y":200,"width":280,"height":350},
		
		{"id":"layer5_group","type":"group","x":-50,"y":1050,"width":1500,"height":700,"label":"5. 评分系统 (Scoring)"},
		{"id":"scoring_paper","type":"text","text":"论文评分 (PaperScorer)\n\n维度 (总分100):\n- A. 信息完备度: 20分\n- B. 预算状态: 不适用\n- C. 决策链条: 15分\n- D. 匹配度: 25分\n- E. 时效性: 20分\n- F. 历史互动: 10分\n- G. 机构类型: 10分\n\n等级区间:\n- A >= 80\n- B = 65-79\n- C = 50-64\n- D < 50\n\n文件：src/scoring/paper_scorer.py","x":-30,"y":1100,"width":700,"height":550},
		{"id":"scoring_tender","type":"text","text":"招标评分 (TenderScorer)\n\n维度 (总分100):\n- A. 信息完备度: 15分\n- B. 预算状态: 20分\n- C. 决策链条: 10分\n- D. 匹配度: 20分\n- E. 时效性: 20分\n- F. 历史互动: 5分\n- G. 机构类型: 10分\n\n等级区间：同论文\n\n文件：src/scoring/tender_scorer.py\n状态：✅ 已实现","x":700,"y":1100,"width":700,"height":550},
		
		{"id":"layer6_group","type":"group","x":1500,"y":1050,"width":500,"height":700,"label":"6. 导出层 (Export)"},
		{"id":"export_csv","type":"text","text":"CSV Exporter\n\n输出格式：\n- PMID | DOI | 文章标题\n- 发表时间 | 通讯作者\n- 单位 | 邮箱\n- 等级 | 分数\n- 来源链接\n\n导出规则：\n- 每日增量导出\n- UTF-8-BOM 编码\n\n文件：src/exporters/csv_exporter.py\n状态：✅ 已实现\n\n输出目录：\noutput/paper_leads/\npaper_leads_YYYY-MM-DD.csv","x":1530,"y":1100,"width":440,"height":600},
		
		{"id":"layer7_group","type":"group","x":-50,"y":1850,"width":1500,"height":600,"label":"7. 通知层 (Notification)"},
		{"id":"notify_feishu","type":"text","text":"Feishu Notifier\n\n功能：\n- Webhook 消息发送\n- 签名校验 (HMAC-SHA256)\n- 每日摘要通知\n- 错误告警\n\n配置：\n- FEISHU_WEBHOOK\n- FEISHU_SECRET\n\n文件：src/notifiers/feishu.py\n状态：✅ 已实现\n\n消息类型：\n- 文本消息\n- 每日摘要\n- 错误通知","x":-30,"y":1900,"width":700,"height":450},
		{"id":"notify_config","type":"text","text":"飞书配置步骤\n\n1. 群聊 → 设置 → 群机器人\n2. 添加自定义机器人\n3. 复制 Webhook URL\n4. 启用签名校验\n5. 复制签名密钥\n6. 配置到 .env:\n   FEISHU_WEBHOOK=...\n   FEISHU_SECRET=...\n\n签名算法：\nstring_to_sign = timestamp + \"\\n\" + secret\nsign = Base64(HmacSHA256(string_to_sign, \"\"))","x":700,"y":1900,"width":700,"height":450},
		
		{"id":"layer8_group","type":"group","x":1500,"y":1850,"width":500,"height":600,"label":"8. 调度层 (Scheduler)"},
		{"id":"scheduler","type":"text","text":"Scheduler\n\n功能：\n- 定时任务调度\n- 每日任务执行\n- 全量/增量导出\n\n配置：\n- SCHEDULE_HOUR=6\n- SCHEDULE_MINUTE=0\n\n任务：\n- run_daily_task()\n- run_full_export()\n\n文件：src/scheduler/scheduler.py\n状态：✅ 已实现\n\n运行时间：\n每日 06:00 启动\n10:00 前完成","x":1530,"y":1900,"width":440,"height":500},
		
		{"id":"workflow_group","type":"group","x":-50,"y":2550,"width":2050,"height":400,"label":"完整工作流程 (Workflow)"},
		{"id":"workflow_steps","type":"text","text":"执行流程\n\n1. 收集 URL (MultiModeCollector)\n   ↓\n2. URL 去重 (URLDeduplicator)\n   ↓\n3. 获取内容 (ContentFetcher)\n   - 优先 Jina Reader\n   - 失败切换 Playwright\n   ↓\n4. LLM 提取 (GLM-5 + Rate Limiter)\n   ↓\n5. 评分 (PaperScorer / TenderScorer)\n   ↓\n6. 入库 (PostgreSQL)\n   ↓\n7. 导出 CSV (CSVExporter)\n   ↓\n8. 飞书通知 (FeishuNotifier)\n\n异常处理：\n- 429 错误自动重试\n- 数据库重复键跳过\n- JSON 解析失败记录","x":-30,"y":2600,"width":2000,"height":300},
		
		{"id":"config_group","type":"group","x":-50,"y":3050,"width":2050,"height":500,"label":"配置管理 (Configuration)"},
		{"id":"config_env","type":"text","text":"环境变量 (.env)\n\n数据库：\n- DATABASE_URL\n\nAPI Keys:\n- JINA_API_KEY\n- ZAI_API_KEY\n- ZAI_MODEL=glm-5\n\n飞书：\n- FEISHU_WEBHOOK\n- FEISHU_SECRET\n\n调度：\n- SCHEDULE_HOUR=6\n- SCHEDULE_MINUTE=0\n\n日志：\n- LOG_LEVEL=INFO\n- LOG_RETENTION_DAYS=30","x":-30,"y":3100,"width":650,"height":350},
		{"id":"config_yaml","type":"text","text":"YAML 配置文件 (config/)\n\nkeywords.yaml:\n- 搜索关键词\n- 招标关键词\n\nsources.yaml:\n- 数据源配置\n- 优先级设置\n\nscoring_paper.yaml:\n- 论文评分权重\n- 等级区间\n\nscoring_tender.yaml:\n- 招标评分权重\n- 等级区间\n\nscheduler.yaml:\n- 定时任务配置","x":650,"y":3100,"width":650,"height":350},
		{"id":"config_loader","type":"text","text":"Config Loader\n\n文件：src/config/loader.py\n\n功能：\n- 加载 .env 环境变量\n- 加载 YAML 配置\n- 统一配置接口\n- 全局单例模式\n\n特性：\n- override=True 强制使用 .env\n- 自动类型转换\n- 默认值回退","x":1330,"y":3100,"width":650,"height":350}
	],
